    "name": "Drow Poison",
    "source": "Dungeon Master’s Guide",
    "sourceUrl": "aurora-elements/core/dungeon-masters-guide/items/items-poison.xml",
    "description": "This poison is typically made only by the draw, and only in a place far removed from sunlight. A creature subjected to this poison must succeed on a DC 13 Constitution saving throw or be poisoned for 1 hour. If the saving throw fails by 5 or more, the creature is also unconscious while poisoned in this way. The creature wakes up if it takes damage or if another creature takes an action to shake it awake.",
